# Generated per-app sidecar compose fragments live here:
# docker/sidecars/<app>.yml, written by scripts/compose.sh on
# `make webpack MODE=<hmr|watch>`, deleted by `MODE=off`, globbed into
# the Makefile $(DC) macro. .gitignore covers `*.yml`, not this file.
#
# This tracked .gitkeep exists so the dir is present (owned by the host
# user) on a fresh clone — otherwise docker's create_host_path:true
# default invents an empty root-owned dir at the first sidecar bind.
